IV. Igitur Archelaum (nam et hic accitus a Taxile in Thessaliam accurrerat) caeteri duces ad praelii tentandam lon tunam indesinenter hortabantur, donec consensu omnium victus, nam trahere bellum haud absurdo consilio statuerat, in aciem suos eduxit.
